## 1. Description of Service
Storentry is a local, offline-first inventory management application designed to help grocery stores, kirana shops, pharmacies, electronics retailers, and small businesses manage products, track stock counts, calculate inventory values, and set low stock alerts in real-time.

---

## 2. Data Ownership and Stewardship
* **Absolute Ownership:** You own 100% of the product listings, pricing data, and transaction information that you input into the application. We make no claims of ownership over your inventory.
* **Offline Responsibility:** Because Storentry runs offline-first, your database is stored on your physical device. If your device is lost, stolen, or broken, and you have not configured a Cloud Backup, Storentry cannot retrieve or restore your unbacked-up data.

---

## 3. Account and Optional Cloud Synchronizations
* **No Account Required:** You can use Storentry completely offline without registering an account.
* **Optional Cloud Sync:** You may choose to sign in via Google using Android\'s Credential Manager. By doing so, you opt-in to secure backups and real-time syncing of your inventory data to Google Firebase Firestore.
* **Fair Use & Sandboxing:** Synced data is completely private to your unique Google authenticated profile. You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality and security of your Google account login.

---

## 4. Subscription Tiers (Storentry Pro)
Storentry offers a Free Tier and a paid Premium Tier (Storentry Pro):
* **Free Tier:** Limited to 100 products and a maximum of 5 active stock update reminders. Cloud backups are performed manually via "Sync Now".
* **Premium Tier (Storentry Pro):** Unlocks unlimited inventory items, advanced analytics reports, and fully automatic real-time cloud backups ("Auto-Sync").
* **Payments & Billing:** Premium billing is processed securely via RevenueCat and Google Play Store billing. Subscriptions auto-renew at the end of each billing period unless cancelled at least 24 hours prior. You can manage or cancel your subscription at any time within your Google Play Store account settings.

